        <description>&lt;p&gt;Happy Lunar Year!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;流程：

&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/framework/open-ability/login.html&#34; 


