&gt;
https://developers.weixin.qq.com/miniprogram/dev/framework/open-ability/login.html
&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;前端获取授权码，向 

&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://api.weixin.qq.com/sns/jscode2session&#34; 


   target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
